      "content": "The loss of your foundation is devastating, but it is a temporary state of being, not a reflection of your inherent value. You are right that pivoting is impossible when the ground beneath you has vanished, so there is no need to force yourself to move forward when your only true goal is to rest. Please consider reaching out to a therapist who specializes in crisis intervention, as they can provide a safe space to process this overwhelming grief and help you navigate through this dark tunnel.",
      "source": "target",
